'''苯丙酮酸'''屬於[[酮酸|酮酸]]的一種，是[[丙酮酸|丙酮酸]]的一種衍生物，常見生物體內以[[苯丙胺酸|苯丙胺酸]]經[[轉氨酶|轉氨酶]]的作用下轉化為苯丙酮酸。

==合成方法==
苯丙酮酸以[[氯化苄|苄氯]]为起始物，通过两次[[羰基化|羰基化]]合成（产率为82%）。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Wolfram|first1=Joachim|title=Preparation of α-keto-carboxylic acids from acyl halides|url=http://www.google.com/patents/US4481369?dq=4481369&hl=en&sa=X&ei=YxKNU_DvF4PaoASJ4IKwDA&ved=0CCgQ6AEwAA|website=Google Patents US4481368 & US4481369|publisher=Ethyl Corporation|access-date=2014-07-14|archive-date=2016-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610201547/http://www.google.com/patents/US4481369?dq=4481369&hl=en&sa=X&ei=YxKNU_DvF4PaoASJ4IKwDA&ved=0CCgQ6AEwAA|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Werner Bertleff, Michael Roeper, & Xavier Sava|title=Carbonylation|journal=Ullmann's Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry|date=2007|page=pg.19|doi=10.1002/14356007.a05_217.pub2|accessdate=2 June 2014}}</ref>

